pages.title: About
pages.text: Actually there’s no much thing to talk about. But anyway. My name is Olive and this is my first personal site. I was born in 2006, an urban child. In 2021, I graduated from The Second Yu Ying Foreign Languages School of Nanjing and started my life in Jinling High School International Department A-Level Centre. Well that’s quite both two long names. I am a 70% INTJ and 30% ENTJ, according to MBTI. I am also a slytherclaw(both Slytherin and Ravenclaw). The reason I call this site “doradolive” is that it contains two names: dorado and olive. Dorado is a Spanish word meaning “golden”, also acts as a name for a marine fish with silver and bright blue coloration when alive. I also considered calling this site “ocellradolive” but that seemed too much. I took interest in Mathematics, Chinese, Economics, Computer Science and Linguistics. I’ll update this page if I want to change anything but for now, that’s all. Welcome.
